From: 3090 team <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: 2026-05-19
Subject: [PATCH] qwen3_5: register MoeForCausalLM + ForCausalLM in EntryClass

SGLang discovers supported model architectures by walking each model
file's module-level `EntryClass` list. Whatever isn't in `EntryClass`
is treated as "no SGLang implementation" even when the class is
defined right there in the file.

`qwen3_5.py` defines four model heads:

  - `Qwen3_5ForCausalLM`               (line 961)   — dense, text-only
  - `Qwen3_5MoeForCausalLM`            (line 1256)  — MoE, text-only
  - `Qwen3_5ForConditionalGeneration`  (line 1466)  — dense, multimodal
  - `Qwen3_5MoeForConditionalGeneration` (line 1661) — MoE, multimodal

…but `EntryClass` only listed the two `ConditionalGeneration` variants.
Result: any Qwen3.5/3.6 checkpoint whose `config.json` declares
`architectures: ["Qwen3_5MoeForCausalLM"]` or `["Qwen3_5ForCausalLM"]`
fails to load:

    ValueError: Qwen3_5MoeForCausalLM has no SGlang implementation and
    the Transformers implementation is not compatible with SGLang.

This is the failure mode we hit on the `qwen36` preset
(`mattbucci/Qwen3.6-35B-A3B-AWQ-CT` declares `Qwen3_5MoeForCausalLM`
in its config; the multimodal mirrors at
`Qwen3.6-35B-A3B-AWQ-native-thinking-vision` still load because they
declare `Qwen3_5MoeForConditionalGeneration`). Also affects
`Qwen3.6-27B-AWQ-CT-balanced` (declares `Qwen3_5ForCausalLM`).

The fix is a straight registration update — `Qwen3_5MoeForCausalLM`
inherits from `Qwen3_5ForCausalLM` and both classes already have
complete `__init__` + `load_weights` + `forward` implementations in
the file. No new code, just expose them to SGLang's model-architecture
registry.

Repro: launch the qwen36 preset at TP=2 with the CT mirror:

    MODEL=$MODELS_DIR/hf-mattbucci/Qwen3.6-35B-A3B-AWQ-CT \
    QUANT=compressed-tensors \
    ./scripts/launch.sh qwen36

Before this patch: ValueError above, cycle exits rc=1 in <1 min.
After this patch: server boots, /health=200, rollouts proceed.

---
 python/sglang/srt/models/qwen3_5.py | 7 ++++++-
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/python/sglang/srt/models/qwen3_5.py b/python/sglang/srt/models/qwen3_5.py
--- a/python/sglang/srt/models/qwen3_5.py
+++ b/python/sglang/srt/models/qwen3_5.py
@@ -1976,4 +1976,9 @@ class Qwen3_5MoeForConditionalGeneration(Qwen3VLForConditionalGeneration):
         )


-EntryClass = [Qwen3_5MoeForConditionalGeneration, Qwen3_5ForConditionalGeneration]
+EntryClass = [
+    Qwen3_5MoeForConditionalGeneration,
+    Qwen3_5MoeForCausalLM,
+    Qwen3_5ForConditionalGeneration,
+    Qwen3_5ForCausalLM,
+]
